# Scene Lab

- Do **not** put look-dev scenery into under_pressure or other full games unless the user asks to export.
- Composition: edit `Code/Scene/WorkbenchScene.cs`
- New reusable geometry: add `Code/Pieces/<Name>Piece.cs` with a static `Build(...)`
- Shared tinted primitives: `Code/Kit/`
- After changes, user opens `scene_lab.sbproj` and plays `scenes/workbench.scene` (R rebuilds)
- Depth: ±1 on coplanar faces; ground sitting via `Depth.CenterLift`
- Units: Source-style (same ballpark as under_pressure scenery — hundreds of units for streets)
